# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Personal OS — .gitignore
#
# This is a PUBLIC repo. It ships the FRAMEWORK only:
# skills, agents, scripts, schemas, templates, docs, and *.example seeds.
#
# Your PERSONAL data (filled-in focus, projects, decisions, task queue) and
# any BUILD/META notes about creating the OS itself stay LOCAL — never pushed.
#
# Fresh clone: `python3 scripts/osctl.py init` recreates the live files from
# the committed *.example templates.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── System / tooling ──
.DS_Store
*.log
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.env
.env.*

# ── Private runtime: handoffs, reflections, telemetry, temp context ──
.os_runtime/

# ── Personal live state (seeded from *.example, kept out of git) ──
os/now.md
os/projects.md
os/02_Planning/Backlog.md
os/02_Planning/Weekly_Plan.md
os/02_Planning/Task_Board.md
os/03_Decisions/Decisions.md
os/03_Decisions/Open_Decisions.md
os/05_Control_Plane/active-work.json

# Generated dated decision briefs (e.g. 2026-06-11-choose-first-project.md)
os/03_Decisions/[0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]-*.md

# Personal project pages — keep only the template and the folder README
os/04_Projects/*
!os/04_Projects/Project_Template.md
!os/04_Projects/README.md

# ── Build / meta notes about creating the OS itself ──
/_meta/
/private/
SESSION_*.md
*.session.md
CONTINUITY.md
*.local.md
*.draft.md
